Wimborne Minster.title: Wimborne Minster
Wimborne Minster.byline: Wimborne Minster, also called just Wimborne, is a town of 16,000 people (2014) at the confluence of the River Stour and the River Allen, on the Dorset Heaths in Dorset, England.

Wimmera.title: Wimmera
Wimmera.byline: The Wimmera is a region in western Victoria, Australia.
